\c 11
\s Kunyengetera.
\s (Mat. 6. 9-13.)
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakati achinyengetera paneimwe nzvimbo, apedza, mumwe wavadzidzi vake akati kwaari: Ishe, tidzidzisei kunyengetera, Johwani sezvaakadzidzisa vadzidzi vake vo.
\v 2 Akati kwavari: Kana muchinyengetera, muti: Baba, vedu vari kudenga zita renyu ngariitwe dzvene; vushe bwenyu ngabwuvuye; kuda kwenyu ngakuitwe panyika sezvakunoitwa kudenga.
\v 3 mutipei zuva rimwe nerimwe zvokudya zvedu zvinotiringana;
\v 4 mutikangamwire zvivi zvedu sesu tichikangamwira vane mhoswa nesu musatiisa pakuidzwa asi mutisunungure pane zvakaipa,
\s Mufananidzo weshamwari yakatsungirira.
\p
\v 5 Akati kwavari: Ndianiko kwamuri ungava neshamwari, akaenda kwaari pakati povusiku, akati kwaari; Shamwari, ndiposevo zvingwa zvitatu;
\v 6 nokuti shamwari yangu iri parwendo yakasvika kwandiri, zvino handina chandingamupakurira.
\v 7 Uri mukati akapindura, akati; Usandinetsa; mukova watopfigwa, navana vangu vava neni panhovo; handingamuki ndikakupa.
\v 8 Ndinoti kwamuri: Kunyange asingamuki akamupa, nokuda kokuti ishamwari yake, kunyange zvakadaro, nokuda kokutsungirira kwake, uchamuka, akamupa zvose zvaanoshaiwa.
\v 9 Ndinoti kwamuri: Kumbirai, muchapiwa; tsvakai, muchawana; gogodzai, muchazarurirwa.
\v 10 Nokuti mumwe nomumwe unokumbira, unopiwa; unotsvaka, unowana; nounogogodza, unozarurirwa.
\v 11 Ndavapiko baba pakati penyu, kana mwanakomana achikumbira chingwa, vangamupa ibwe here? Kana hove, vangamupa nyoka panzvimbo yehove here?
\v 12 Kana akakumbira zai, vangamupa chinyavada here?
\v 13 Naizvozvo kana imi makaipa muchiziva kupa vana venyu zvipo zvakanaka, Baba venyu vari kudenga vachapa zvikuru sei Mweya Mutsvene vanokumbira kwaari.
\s Jesu unobudisa mweya yakaipa, Unodadirwa navaFarisi.
\s (Mat. 12. 22-37.)
\p
\v 14 Zvino wakanga achibudisa mweya wakaipa, waiva mbeveve; mweya wakaipa ukati wabva, mbeveve ikataura, vanhu vazhinji vakashamiswa.
\v 15 Asi vamwe vavo vakati: Unobudisa mweya yakaipa naBheerizebhuri, mukuru wemweya yakaipa.
\v 16 Asi vamwe vakamuidza, vakakumbira chiratidzo kwaari chinobva kudenga.
\v 17 Zvino iye wakati achiziva kufunga kwavo, akati kwavari; Vushe bwumwe nobwumwe bwunozvipesanisa, bwunoparadzwa; neimba inozvipesanisa inowa.
\v 18 NaSatani, kana achizvipesanisa, vushe bwake bwungamira seiko, zvamunoti, ndinobudisa mweya yakaipa naBheerizebhuri?
\v 19 Kana ini ndichibudisa mweya yakaipa naBheerizebhuri, ko vanakomana venyu vanoibudisa nani? Naizvozvo ivo vachava vatongi venyu.
\v 20 Asi kana ndichibudisa mweya yakaipa nomumwe waMwari, ipapo vushe bwaMwari bwasvika kwamuri.
\v 21 Kana munhu unesimba, wakashonga nhumbi dzokurwa, achirinda imba yake, nhumbi dzake dzinochengeteka.
\v 22 Asi kana mumwe unomupfuvura nesimba akamuvamba, akamukunda, ipapo uchamutorera nhumbi dzose dzokurwa, dzaakanga achivimba nadzo, ndokugovera izvo zvaapamba.
\v 23 Usineni, unopesana neni, nousingavunganidzi neni, unoparadza.
\v 24 Kana mweya wetsvina wabuda kumunhu, unopota nenzvimbo dzakawoma, uchitsvaka zororo; kana ukashaiwa, unoti: Ndichadzokera kumba kwangu kwandakabuda.
\v 25 Kana wasvika, unoiwana yatsvairwa, yagadzirwa.
\v 26 Ipapo unoenda, ndokundotora mimwe mweya minomwe inoukunda pakuipa, ndokupinda, ndokugaramo; kuguma komunhu uyo \add kwakaipa \add*kupfuvura kutanga kwake.
\v 27 Wakati areva izvozvo, mumwe mukadzi pakati pegurumwandira akasimudza inzwi rake, akati kwaari: Rakaropafadzwa dumbu rakakutakura, namazamu amakamwa.
\v 28 Asi iye akati: Hongu, asi zvikuru vakaropafadzwa vanonzwa shoko raMwari, vachirichengeta.
\s Chiratidzo chomuporofita Jona
\p
\v 29 Zvino gurumwandira rakati richivunganira kwaari, akatanga kuti: Urwu, rudzi rwakaipa; runotsvaka chiratidzo, asi hakuna chiratidzo charungapiwa asi chiratidzo chomuporofita Jona.
\v 30 Nokuti Jona sezvaakanga ari chiratidzo kuvaNinivhi, ndizvo zvichaitavo Mwanakomana womunhu kurudzi urwu.
\v 31 Mambokadzi wekuchamhembe uchasimuka pakutonga navarume vorudzi urwu, akavapa mhosva, nokuti wakabva pamigumo yenyika, kuzonzwa kuchenjera kwaSoromoni; tarirai, mukuru kunaSoromoni pano.
\v 32 Varume veNinivhi vachasimuka pakutonga norudzi urwu, vakarupa mhosva, nokuti vakatendevuka pakuparidza kwaJona; zvino tarirai, mukuru kunaJona pano.
\s Mufananidzo womwenje
\p
\v 33 Hakunomunhu unoti kana atungidza mwenje, ungaisa pakavanda, kana pasi pedengu, asi pachigadziko chemwenje, kuti vanopinda vavone chiedza.
\v 34 Mwenje womuviri iziso rako; naizvozvo kana ziso rako rakanaka, muviri wako wose uchazara nechiedza; asi kana rakaipa, muviri wako wose uchazara nerima.
\v 35 Naizvozvo chenjera kuti chiedza chiri mukati mako chirege kuva rima.
\v 36 Zvino kana muviri wako wose wakavhenekerwa, pasinarutivi runerima, uchavhenekerwa wose, somwenje unokuvhenekera nokupenya kwawo.
\s Jesu unotuka vaFarisi navadudziri vomurairo.
\s (Mat. 23. 13-35.)
\p
\v 37 Wakati achataura, mumwe muFarisi akakumbira kwaari kuti asvusvure naye; akapinda, akagara pakudya.
\v 38 Zvino muFarisi akashamiswa, achivona kuti haana kumboshamba asati asvusvura.
\v 39 Ishe akati kwaari: Zvino imi vaFarisi, munosuka kunze komukombe nendiro, asi mukati menyu muzere nokukara nokuipa.
\v 40 Imi mapenzi! Ko uyo wakaita zviri kunze, haazi iye wakaita zviri mukati vo here.
\v 41 Asi zviri nani mupe zvipo pazvinhu zvamunazvo; ipapo tarirai zvose zvichava zvakanaka kwamuri.
\v 42 Asi munenhamo, imi vaFarisi, nokuti munopa chegumi cheminte neruyi nemirivo yose, muchirega kururamisira mhaka norudo kunaMwari; maifanira kuzviita izvi, nokusarega kuita izvozvo.
\v 43 Munenhamo, imi vaFaraise, nokuti munoda zvigaro zvapamberi mumasinagoge, nokukwaziswa padare.
\v 44 Munenhamo, imi, nokuti makaita samarinda asingavonekwi; vanhu vanofamba pamusoro pawo, vasingazivi.
\v 45 Zvino mumwe wavadudziri vomurairo wakapindura, akati kwaari: Mudzidzisi, kana muchitaura izvozvo, munotituka nesuvo.
\v 46 Iye akati: Mune nhamo nemi vo, vadudziri vomurairo; nokuti munotakudza vanhu mitoro inorema, inotambudza kutakura, asi imi mumene hamubati mitoro iyo kunyange nomumwe wenyu mumwe.
\v 47 Munenhamo, imi, nokuti munovaka marinda avaporofita vakavurawa namadzibaba enyu.
\v 48 Naizvozvo muri zvapupu, kana muchitenderana namabasa amadzibaba enyu; nokuti ivo vakavavuraya, nemi munovaka marinda avo.
\v 49 Saka nokuchenjera kwaMwarivo akati: Ndichatumira kwavari vaporofita navapositora, vachavuraya vamwe vavo, nokuvatambudza;
\v 50 kuti mhosva yeropa ravaporofita vose, rakatevurwa kubva pakuvambwa kwenyika, itsvakwe parudzi urwu;
\v 51 kubva paropa raAberi, kusvikira paropa raZakaria, wakavurawa pakati pearitari neImba yaMwari;hongu, ndinoti kwamuri mhosva ichatsvakwa parudzi urwu.
\v 52 Munenhamo, imi vadudziri vomurairo; nokuti makabvisa kiyi yokuziva; hamuna kupinda mumene, vuye makadzivisa avo vakanga vachida kupinda.
\v 53 Wakati achibvapo vanyori navaFarisi vakatanga kumumanikidza kwazvo, nokumubvunzisisa pamusoro pezvimwe zvizhinji,
\v 54 vachimurindira, kuti vamubate pashoko rinobuda mumuromo make.
